{"tid":1669331,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"借九成 - 左丁山","createTime":"2019-10-22T13:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T13:27:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09aca5454ef3902bc9c631748888d496b6e37074","tid":1669331,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%B7%A6%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%B1/daily/article/20191022/20791135/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%25B1%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F20791135%2F&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=1a5339c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E4%25B8%2581%25E5%25B1%25B1%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F20791135%2F&h=5f92d1de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%B7%A6%E4%B8%81%E5%B1%B1/daily/article/20191022/20791135/</a><br />\n<br />\n借九成 - 左丁山<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191022/large/1571642367_d3f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191022%2Flarge%2F1571642367_d3f5.jpg&h=a8b7f566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世姪B與左丁山在中環天橋相遇，話想參加網上號召到重慶大廈示威，抗議南亞裔襲擊及重傷岑子杰，左丁山叫佢千萬唔好，因涉及種族衝突，事件可大可小，到時示威者作出歧視行動，叫出歧視口號，咁就會畀藍絲作大新聞，國際上亦唔會諒解，保加利亞對英格蘭場足球賽就是前車可鑒。<br />\n<br />\n世姪B當時冇話唔去示威，但到咗晚上，佢來短訊：「太高興，同女朋友食完晚飯，佢話趁政府推出首置可以借九成，叫我為結婚籌謀，一於買樓借足九成，女朋友亦係做銀行，兩個人薪水加埋可以應付壓力測試，橫掂我地唔夠首期，今勻可以借九成，機會難逢也，你認為點睇？」<br />\n<br />\n於是打電話畀佢：「你想點呀？」世姪B話：「女朋友都有示威遊行過，但我地唔係衝衝子，呢次有機會買樓借九成，佢驚住我地是但一個在街頭被捕，壞了結婚計劃好事，所以唔去示威咯。你亦講得啱，我銀行都有南亞裔同事，佢地同胞斬人，點可以扯埋佢地落水，要分開嚟講。」<br />\n<br />\n有人話林鄭月娥之首置借九成，根本係陽謀，利誘和理非有能力買樓一族退出示威行列，以後二三十年為了供樓，行動不會過激。無論陰謀陽謀，香港係有不少28至32歲年青專業人士，如會計師嫁醫生，律師娶銀行主任，工程師娶建築師等等，兩人月薪加埋起碼在七萬八萬以上，或係十幾萬，不靠父幹，絕對有能力供樓，但冇足夠五成首期（現時金管局限制），借九成喎，根本係為呢班人度身定做，去年年底陳茂波曾有此議，即刻畀林鄭否決，到現在，林鄭唔會記得自己講過乜嘅嘞，一於派糖利誘和理非唔好上街先。施政報告一出，美聯地產股價立即上揚，就係呢種心理預期嘅反映。講到賣樓時間之精準，長實真係第一，可以揀正施政報告推出後開賣新樓盤，問你服未，超人之眼光，係零舍高啲，譬如長實以天價（400億以上）賣出中環中心，交易完成後，中環甲級商廈價格有跌冇升，又逢林鄭心急，搞到香港亂晒龍，高昂租金支持唔住嘞，中環中心新業主唯有短炒變長揸，證明超人能夠摸頂出貨，凡人炒家就摸頂入貨。<br />\n<br />\n左丁山知道世姪B想趁機買現樓做其首置業主，走去問地產專家王震宇點睇，佢大潑冷水：「因住負資產，你問我，我睇樓價會繼續下跌，唔好咁快跌落林鄭陷阱！」於是又講番畀世姪B聽，請佢自行考慮清楚。 <br />\n<br />\n左丁山<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"166bfa8ed4a9e9cc8e3f644122810bec5313fda7","tid":1669331,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"阿香ＳＩＲ香恕輝Ｄ垃圾文就無謂提真係"},{"pid":"4cdebc8f117f20dc67931ec9b3ff797d9ed21505","tid":1669331,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"今時今日會買樓都係傻鳩<br />\n中美貿易戰只會搞到中港經濟一年比一年差，仲未計中國人口老化、人工高企... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國氣數已盡架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3b475ed023a8decf21b3b1a1feef1199491ecd","tid":1669331,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"//...<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">借九成</span></span></strong>喎，根本係為呢班人度身定做，去年年底陳茂波曾有此議，即刻畀林鄭否決，到現在，林鄭唔會記得自己講過乜嘅嘞，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一於派糖利誘</span></span></strong>和理非唔好上街先。...//<br />\nCLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8924f94ebe75428115d12ec061060f15d5e44b","tid":1669331,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"瑞銀房地產研究部前主管王震宇<br />\nUBS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n早幾年UBS、Deutsche Bank日撚日話樓價跌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無供應撚會跌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你DB執撚晒成個equity department都未撚跌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}